column5: I'm trying to find directions to the Olympiad in Etobicoke. I think its off Burnamthorpe. I cant seem to be able to find directions there.
It's right around the corner from me.  It's called the Etobicoke Olympium, at the northwest corner of Renforth and Rathburn.
i work there here is the link  Etobicoke Olympium 590 Rathburn Rd Etobicoke, ON
